Verse 26 says,

00:08:06.860 --> 00:08:08.860
Be wrathful but do not sin.

00:08:08.860 --> 00:08:12.860
Do not let the sun set while you are still angry.

00:08:12.860 --> 00:08:14.860
And here's the point.

00:08:14.860 --> 00:08:18.860
